Class ArgumentType

java.lang.Object
org.freedesktop.dbus.messages.constants.ArgumentType
public final class ArgumentType extends Object
Defines constants for each argument type. There are two constants for each argument type, as a byte or as a String (the _STRING version)
Since:
5.0.0 - 2023-10-23
